OL,3,CInvestigation underway after large
OL,4,Cscale steelworks fire
OL,6,FAn investigation into the cause of the
OL,7,Ffire at Port Talbot Steelworks is
OL,8,Funderway.
OL,10,FFire services were called to the
OL,11,Fsteelworks on June 3, following a
OL,12,Flarge-scale fire inside an industrial
OL,13,Fstructure. 16 local fire crews tackled
OL,14,Fthe blaze.
OL,16,FThe company says the build of the new
OL,17,FElectric Arc Furnace (EAF), which had
OL,18,Falready been delayed, has not been
OL,19,Ffurther impacted.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
