OL,3,CInvestigation underway after large
OL,4,Cscale steelworks fire
OL,6,FIn a bid to reassure customers and
OL,7,Fmanufacturers, Tata Steel says
OL,8,Fmitigation measures have been put in
OL,9,Fplace to maintain supply; including
OL,10,Fthe use of the Llanwern Pickle line,
OL,11,Frestarting the Llanwern Cold Mill, and
OL,12,Ffurther support from the wider Tata
OL,13,FSteel Group.
OL,15,FThe company says stock levels are
OL,16,Fhealthy and Hot Strip Mill operations
OL,17,Fat Port Talbot have now resumed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
