OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781704085
OL,3,CInvestigation underway after large
OL,4,Cscale steelworks fire
OL,6,FRajesh Nair, CEO of Tata Steel UK
OL,7,Fsaid: "Based on our current
OL,8,Fassessments, we remain confident in
OL,9,Four ability to continue supporting
OL,10,Fcustomers and downstream manufacturers
OL,11,Fduring this period and do not
OL,12,Fcurrently expect significant market-
OL,13,Fwide disruption.
OL,15,F'The long-term transformation of Port
OL,16,FTalbot remains absolutely central to
OL,17,Four future plans and the wider
OL,18,FElectric Arc Furnace project continues
OL,19,Fto progress at pace".
