OL,3,CInvestigation underway after large
OL,4,Cscale steelworks fire
OL,6,FEmergency crews from Mid and West
OL,7,FWales Fire worked through the night
OL,8,Fwhen the fire broke out at the Cold
OL,9,FMill area of the Port Talbot
OL,10,Fsteelworks, with 8 fire appliances and
OL,11,Faround 100 responders on the scene.
OL,13,FA spokesperson at MAWW Fire Service
OL,14,Fsaid the investigation is still
OL,15,Fongoing.
